'''约瑟琳·芭芭拉·赫普沃斯'''女爵士，[[DBE|DBE]]（{{lang|en|'''Dame Jocelyn Barbara Hepworth'''}}，{{bd|1903年|1月10日|1975年|5月20日|catIdx=H}}），[[英国|英国]][[现代主义|现代主义]]艺术家和[[雕塑家|雕塑家]]。赫普沃斯与{{le|本·尼科尔森|Ben Nicholson}}、{{le|瑙姆·加博|Naum Gabo}}一道，是[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间英国[[圣艾夫斯_(康沃尔郡)|圣艾夫斯]]艺术家群体中的领军人物<ref name=gale>Gale, Matthew [http://www.tate.org.uk/art/artists/dame-barbara-hepworth-1274 "Artist Biography: Barbara Hepworth 1903–75"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tate.org.uk/art/artists/dame-barbara-hepworth-1274 |date=20180107061007 }} Retrieved 31 January 2014.</ref>。

赫普沃斯1903年出生于[[约克郡|约克郡]]西部的[[韦克菲尔德|韦克菲尔德]]，是家中长女。1920年，赫普沃斯进入[[利兹艺术大学|利兹艺术学院]]学习，在那里认识了同为现代主义雕塑家的[[亨利·摩尔|亨利·摩尔]]<ref name=bio>[http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/biography/ Barbara Hepworth: Biography] {{Wayback|url=http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/biography/ |date=20160211184438 }}. Hepworth Estate.  Retrieved 31 January 2014</ref>，他们建立起深厚的友谊，并在后来保持了多年的友好竞争关系。1921年，赫普沃斯进入[[伦敦|伦敦]]的[[皇家艺术学院|皇家艺术学院]]深造，1924年取得文凭<ref name=ccc>{{cite web|url=http://www.cornwall.gov.uk/index.cfm?articleid=29038|archive-url=https://archive.is/20071025033707/http://www.cornwall.gov.uk/index.cfm?articleid=29038|archivedate=2007-10-25|title=Barbara Hepworth|year=2007|publisher=Cornwall County Council |accessdate=2014-02-01}}</ref>。1939年[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]开始后，赫普沃斯搬至英格兰西南部的[[康沃尔郡|康沃尔郡]]居住<ref name=tate>[http://www.tate.org.uk/visit/tate-st-ives/barbara-hepworth-museum-and-sculpture-garden About Barbara Hepworth Museum and Sculpture Garden] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tate.org.uk/visit/tate-st-ives/barbara-hepworth-museum-and-sculpture-garden |date=20200820200505 }}. Tate St Ives. Retrieved 31 January 2014.</ref>，1949年迁至[[圣艾夫斯_(康沃尔郡)|圣艾夫斯]]的特雷温工作室（Trewyn studios）。1975年5月20日，特雷温工作室发生火灾，赫普沃斯在火灾中罹难，享年72岁<ref name="barbarahepworth.org">{{cite web|last1=Bowness|first1=Sophie|title=Biography|url=http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/biography/|website=barbarahepworth.org.uk|publisher=Sophie Bowness|accessdate=2016-02-11|archive-date=2016-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160211184438/http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/biography/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其后，特雷温工作室以及她的住宅被建为{{le|芭芭拉·赫普沃斯博物馆|Barbara Hepworth Museum}}，1980年起由[[泰特美术馆|泰特美术馆]]所有<ref name=gale/>。

赫普沃斯其中一件最具声望的作品是《{{le|单一形式|Single Form}}》<ref name=bio2>{{cite web |url=http://www.barbarahepworth.org.uk/commissions/list/single-form.html |title=Commissions: ''Single Form'' |publisher=Hepworth Estate |accessdate=2014-01-29 |archive-date=2014-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117035032/http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/commissions/list/single-form.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，这是一件青铜雕塑，为纪念她的朋友兼收藏者、[[联合国秘书长|联合国前秘书长]][[达格·哈马舍尔德|达格·哈马舍尔德]]而作，1964年竖立在[[美国|美国]][[纽约|纽约]][[联合国总部大楼|联合国总部大楼]]前<ref name=guardian>MacCarthy, Fiona.[https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2003/may/17/art.artsfeatures "The ambition of Barbara Hepworth"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2003/may/17/art.artsfeatures |date=20191004000951 }} ''The Guardian'', Retrieved 31 January 2014.</ref>。

1958年，赫普沃斯获颁[[大英帝国勋章|大英帝国司令勋章]]（CBE），1965年荣膺爵级司令勋章（DBE）<ref name=alan>Bowness, Alan ([n.d.]). [http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/about-barbara-hepworth/alan-bowness-life-and-work.html ''Life and Work''] {{Wayback|url=http://barbarahepworth.org.uk/about-barbara-hepworth/alan-bowness-life-and-work.html |date=20140201193001 }}. Hepworth Estate. Retrieved 31 January 2014.</ref><ref name=gazette>{{London Gazette |issue=43667 |date= 1965-06-04|page=5480 |supp=y}}</ref>，1973年被选为[[美国艺术暨文学学会|美国艺术暨文学学会]]荣誉会员<ref name=aaal>[http://www.artsandletters.org/academicians2_deceased.php#h Deceased Members: Deceased Foreign Honorary Members] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726004624/http://www.artsandletters.org/academicians2_deceased.php |date=2011-07-26 }}. American Academy of Arts and Letters. Retrieved 31 January 2014.</ref>。

